ZH: 1. 他们设法制止了暴力行为。
EN: They tried to stop the violence.
ZH: 2. 我们需要采取措施来制止环境破坏。
EN: We need to take measures to prevent environmental damage.
ZH: 3. 警察制止了示威者的暴力行动。
EN: The police put an end to the violent actions of the protesters.
ZH: 4. 这位教练严厉地制止了队员们的不良行为。
EN: The coach sternly stopped the players' misconduct.
ZH: 5. 我们必须制止这个问题的进一步恶化。
EN: We must put a stop to the further deterioration of this problem.
ZH: 6. 这场疫情需要全社会共同制止。
EN: This epidemic needs to be collectively stopped by the whole society.
ZH: 7. 政府要采取严厉的措施制止恐怖主义行为。
EN: The government has to take strict measures to prevent terrorist acts.
ZH: 8. 我们需要加强执法来制止违法行为。
EN: We need to strengthen law enforcement to curb illegal activities.
ZH: 9. 这部电影展示了人们如何制止全球暖化。
EN: This movie shows how people can halt global warming.
ZH: 10. 经过多次努力，终于成功制止了这场战争。
EN: After multiple efforts, the war was finally stopped successfully.
ZH: 11. 学校对欺凌行为采取了严厉的制止措施。
EN: The school took strict measures to stop bullying behavior.
ZH: 12. 飞机上的乘务员迅速制止了一个携带炸药的旅客。
EN: The flight attendants swiftly stopped a passenger carrying explosives.
ZH: 13. 家长们集体出面制止了校园内的暴力行为。
EN: The parents collectively intervened to stop the violence on campus.
ZH: 14. 许多人上街示威，要求政府制止种族歧视。
EN: Many people took to the streets to demand that the government stop racial discrimination.
ZH: 15. 这个组织致力于制止童工现象的发生。
EN: This organization is committed to preventing child labor.
ZH: 16. 操场上的老师制止了两个学生的争吵。
EN: The teacher on the playground halted the argument between two students.
ZH: 17. 他们通过信函制止了对方的不当行为。
EN: They stopped each other's misconduct through letters.
ZH: 18. 公司采取了多项措施制止员工的内部泄密行为。
EN: The company took multiple measures to prevent internal leaks of information by employees.
ZH: 19. 这位领导采取了果断行动，制止了员工的不当举动。
EN: The leader took decisive action to stop the employees' misconduct.
ZH: 20. 他们希望能与其他国家合作，制止全球贸易不公平现象。
EN: They hope to cooperate with other countries to restrain unfair global trade practices.
